\begin_layout Standard
We created the sensors with a wearable form factor in mind.
 Since we used Tobe in public settings, it was important that the sensors
 were non-invasive (no need to remove clothes or apply gel to the skin)
 and be quick to install and remove, while being able to acquire a reliable
